    Title: The Trader's Ledger
    Summary: Buy Wren's basket and establish a regular route through Hollowfen.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: theoCapitalOffer
    Title: Theo's Capital
    Summary: Offer Wren a larger market and state its cost plainly.
  _quotes:
  - Text: Cruel answer. I respect it.
    Context: When Wren says she found Goldfoot near trees.
  - Text: When it saves time.
    Context: Explaining his selective honesty.
  - Text: It would cost Hollowfen you.
    Context: Making his Capital offer cleanly.
